## Privacy Notice

AGI Assistant is designed with privacy as a core principle:

- **Local Processing Only**: All data processing occurs on your local machine
- **No Cloud Uploads**: Your data never leaves your computer
- **User Control**: You have complete control over your data
- **Transparent Operation**: All data storage and processing is documented
- **Optional Features**: All data collection features can be disabled

## Data Handling

The software may collect and store locally:
- Screenshots of your desktop (when enabled)
- Audio recordings (when enabled)
- Application usage patterns
- User interaction data

All data is stored locally on your machine and is never transmitted to external servers.

